---
---
<section class="section mission-section" id="mission">
  <div class="mission-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mission-grid">
      <!-- Left: Vision -->
      <div class="mission-left reveal">
        <div class="mission-badge">HIS VISION & MISSION</div>
        <h2 class="mission-title">
          Where <span class="text-gradient">Function</span> Meets<br/>Human Dignity
        </h2>
        <blockquote class="vision-quote">
          "To build a world where brain and functional care isn't limited by geography or wealth — where we may not cure everyone, but we give our all to each one."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="mission-text">
          Dr. Sharan stands for <strong>effort as much as excellence</strong> — for showing up, skillfully and sincerely, in every case, every day. He knows what many won't say aloud: "We may not win every time — but we never stop fighting."
        </p>

        <div class="stands-for">
          <div class="sf-title">What He Stands For</div>
          <ul class="sf-list">
            <li><span class="sf-dot"></span>Healing patients with precision neuromodulation & cutting-edge functional neurosurgery</li>
            <li><span class="sf-dot"></span>Combining advanced neurorehabilitation with technology to help people walk, speak, and live again</li>
            <li><span class="sf-dot"></span>Delivering affordable gold standards of care so every life has access to hope</li>
            <li><span class="sf-dot"></span>Democratizing healthcare — making world-class functional neuroscience inclusive and accessible</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Mission cards -->
      <div class="mission-right">
        <div class="mission-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="mc-icon">🎯</div>
          <h3>His Mission</h3>
          <p>To heal, to restore, and to innovate — for the one patient in front of him, and for the millions waiting in silence.</p>
          <ul class="mc-list">
            <li>Treat using state-of-the-art neuromodulation techniques</li>
            <li>Build integrated rehab ecosystems that make recovery continuous</li>
            <li>Use technology to make care more human and accessible</li>
            <li>Mentor the next generation of clinicians who care deeply</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-card carepare-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="mc-icon">🧩</div>
          <h3>CAREPa-Re™ Framework</h3>
          <p>Dr. Sharan's first-of-its-kind evidence-based analytical matrix — making the unmeasurable, measurable in functional neuroscience.</p>
          <div class="carepare-pills">
            <span class="pill">C — Clinical</span>
            <span class="pill">A — Anatomical</span>
            <span class="pill">R — Radiological</span>
            <span class="pill">EPa — Etio-pathological</span>
            <span class="pill accent-pill">Re — Rehabilitation strategies</span>
          </div>
          <p class="carepare-sub">Now at the core of <strong>newro LOGICS</strong> — turning brain profiles into data, and data into decisions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-card neuro-octane reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="mc-icon">🚀</div>
          <h3>The Neuro-Octane Model</h3>
          <p>Dr. Sharan's larger vision for transforming global neurocare — Function-first Neuroscience, AI-driven patient-specific therapy, and rehabilitation that is intelligent, affordable, and inclusive.</p>
          <div class="octane-tag">His Legacy in Motion</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission-section {
    background: #0f172a;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .mission-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(at 80% 20%, rgba(79,70,229,0.12) 0, transparent 55%),
                radial-gradient(at 20% 80%, rgba(6,182,212,0.08) 0, transparent 55%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .mission-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 72px;
    align-items: start;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .mission-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2);
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,70,229,0.3);
  }

  .mission-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .vision-quote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-color);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
  }

  .mission-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .mission-text strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }

  .stands-for { margin-top: 8px; }

  .sf-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .sf-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .sf-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .sf-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: var(--accent-color);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 7px;
  }

  /* Right: Mission Cards */
  .mission-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .mission-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 32px;
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
  }

  .mission-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-color: rgba(79,70,229,0.4);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .mc-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  .mission-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .mission-card p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .mission-card p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .mc-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .mc-list li {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .mc-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  /* CAREPa-Re */
  .carepare-card {
    background: rgba(79,70,229,0.08);
    border-color: rgba(79,70,229,0.25);
  }

  .carepare-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  .pill {
    padding: 5px 12px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .accent-pill {
    background: rgba(6,182,212,0.15);
    border-color: rgba(6,182,212,0.35);
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .carepare-sub {
    font-size: 0.85rem !important;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .carepare-sub strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }

  /* Neuro-Octane */
  .neuro-octane {
    background: rgba(126,34,206,0.1);
    border-color: rgba(126,34,206,0.25);
  }

  .octane-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    background: var(--premium-gradient);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-top: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .mission-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }
    .mission-left { text-align: center; }
    .vision-quote { text-align: left; }
    .sf-list { text-align: left; }
    .mission-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mission-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .mission-card { padding: 24px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .mission-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .pill { font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 4px 10px; }
  }
</style>
